{"tid":452640,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登有愛」11月去韓國","createTime":"2017-10-30T12:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T21:13:07.000Z","uid":75641,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34b0e1409bb6a56de4a5cfb466a339d1fa5c788c","tid":452640,"uid":75641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"本身11月尾 同朋友買左機票酒店去韓國5日4夜<br />\n<br />\n本身佢去過幾次又有經驗 諗住唔洗plan<br />\n<br />\n點知依家佢甩底 反埋面<br />\n<br />\n求巴打絲打 推介 值得行既地方/食野地方/影相景點<br />\n<br />\n另外 有興趣去既都可以tg 我 <br />\n<br />\n你自己買張機票就得 因為機票跟名無得轉<br />\n<br />\n利申 24男  想搵返同年紀既男/女去 <br />\n<br />\n有興趣既<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/lihkgtrip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Flihkgtrip&d=VwsAVJ4%2Fp%2B1fcv%2Bs%2B2SN9sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=876b4590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/lihkgtrip</a>"},{"pid":"49db21f6e3d691d264bfe6fad9e6fe4f02fc7dbe","tid":452640,"uid":75641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b5a8fa93dd22df10200ac8784c96aaf6e9643f","tid":452640,"uid":75641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"再推 😩求行程推介"},{"pid":"dfbb8403e6eb24cc2494d97bc809db9540ebf0ce","tid":452640,"uid":75824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01aab2546fa815bc23486f918c83a4234ef5dbf3","tid":452640,"uid":2161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"韓國咁撚大你唔講邊到 濟洲又韓國 首爾又韓國點推薦比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7927e6abbb98